iving backward. Hence The St Sophia prophecies. What \"Tears\" contains is OCCP (that space-time.) In 2-74 I remembered it, + in 3-74 (when Thomas took over) I saw it. i ergo, I saw OCCP. OCCP is Thomas' world. Apostolic Xtians don't drive cars. h Thomas' memory: violent revolutionary 3-74: starting with return of dissociated to memory in 2-74: 1) info dump in my head. Written pages - technical. 2) other personality with dissociated (from me) memories: very active + shrewd personality 3) memories of being a violent revolutionary against a repressive regeeme. Us seen that way. philosophic 4) Basic worldview of Hegel-Engels dialectic 5) letter from red army intelligence officer urgent importance 6) dreams of meeting a woman - shown photos of her: \"She will contact you; very important\" 9) spacial augmentation suspesting right brain dominance. The Bob-fred plot in \"Scanner.\" 8) sup you see, item five overcomes the objection that It's all in my head all subjective: 1) a religious or 2/psychotic experience. 8) delusional post-hypnotic ational that I was undergoing a mystic religious theophany âž€ What I call \"anamnesis\" may have been restoration of dissociated memory - I do a ve 73 9) The AI voice. Foreign language - thinking in a language I don't know. Greek elements in it may just indicate scientific terms - which fits in with the scientific + technical pages. 10) Some kind of code in \"Tears\" + us army intelligence interested in it 11) Lem trying to get me to go behind the Iron curtain. This breaks down. 12) sodium pentathol the day my dissociated memory returned. If there were dissociated memories you could predict (as Hal did) that of they could be retrieved it would occur under pentathol for obvious reasons (\"the truth drug\"). Memories of \"a long time ago\" + \"another place\" yet, oddly, visually syntonic (a month later when the full memorie + the other personality broke through). So it was this place + this time viewed another way, viewed by someone who 