nment to those investigating it My group (secret group here in the enemy camp, the us) is the vanguard + instrument of progressive history: its active, organized agent. But of course this is all religious stuff - done as the \"will of God, to fulfill plan\" + usher in a paradise o od's secret where t in dreams we who are secret agents here in the camp of the enemy are reached by motorized (tank) columns, men in uniforms soldiers fully armed, from \"outsides who with punish \"James James; the madman in charge here.\" This is not espionage. This is revolution. The writter pages are instructions. To me. As my real self emerges, to fight the us government as part of the revolutionary attack against it. I see as Cabbala on the far wall: Olive Holt My battle plans - my signal to act - have come. At last [Note after 40 years - this goes back to my childhood. Doesn't this alive Holt cypher - + the Xerox letter itself - conflict with a religious explanation? But even it assumes a mystic aspect: the cabbala, the Hebrew letters trans‐ form. Everything is seen by me under the aspect of religion - due to the Golden Fish sign. ➀ No - the plans are in my head, the signal is: all that written signal to remember + to act. stuff + photographs, entering my mind \"from my outside\" - i.e. from a dissociated part of brain. Right hemisphere, sensed as coming from the OCCP. Olive Holt - this tells it all. But this is a Holy revolution, against oppression, tyranny, slavement: the old \"Roman\" Empire. If it was religious why did I sense occp from the very start, + specifically taking control of me, assuming power over me to make he into a machine that did what it wantel? Reducing me to robot status against my will. answering that ad that + showed the hasetaly + sickle - that's when compe being programmed by OCCP. that I could be made to do anything, + it wasn't good - + so called the Fullerton PD, + told then I was a machine under OCCP control\" + to lock me up for the good of the U.S. I was fighting it off as best I could. I got the Xerox missive to the Bureau; that was my shot fired off as I fell mortally wounded (by OCCP) - my return fire in defense. I didn't know what the Xerox missive was because God told me; I knew because I knew (re the AI voice late last year). (The AI voice saying what it did showed that on a subliminal level I knew it was \"from an intelligence officer in the army.\" That was my dissociated self thinking, I finally managed to transliminate in 978 knowledge which was there in '74 + before. army\" fits in with the Palm tree AFBIKA corps in the James-James dream. A military invasion is alluded to, that in the final analysis \"the liberators\" are military + uniformed + mechanized in nature: quite modern. A modern day army. fast moving: gliding swiftly + silently in the liberate \"Prisoners\" who are spell bound by sames the James who is insane. (demented monarch - like George its vs the American colonists! Only this time instead of breaking free of him we overthrow him, as cromwell did king James \"Scanner,\" written mainly before 2-3-74 shows the degradation of a person with two \"warring hemispheres\" employed 1) by political forces he doesn't know about 2) for purposes he does not - cannot - understand. His reduc to a reflex machine. + I wrote that last part at new path, before 2-3-74 inc his final triumph: firing off that one lethal vengeful return shot before he succumbs h s te + 1 book as prima facie evidence that a spiritual religion was not involved in 2-3-74 but anstead bitter, cruel, practical, powerful mundane forces: \"the Government,\" as I put it in \"Scanner. A cynical ruthless government had so made use of him without his knowledge or consent - yet, despite the justice of it, it was necessary, because the task involved penetration of the enemy's domain territory - by a spy, a secret agent, who of necessity could himself not know 1) that he was a secret agent or 2) what his mission was. He acted on subcortical reflex. (+ this was written before 2-3-74. They had programmed him, fucked him over. How could I have known to write this? The answer is obvious. the missing pieces - the religious \"explanation deliberate comingling appears in \"Faith of...\" of God + communism. + something to do with drugs Scanner\" shows how bitterly (before 2-3-74!) I resented what had been done to me - this shows up in the last sections of the novel us tie tely is the attitude which caused me to burn Thomas by contacting the Bureau. Now, it seems impossible that that had been written before 2-3-74, but it was. Just before. e I figured it out. The sodium pentathol + golden Fish were unplanned (obviously, at least by mundane agencies). But the combination caused the dissociation to begin to break down - + added the religious aspect - quite by chance. I wasn't supposed to remember - until the Xerox missive came, + then I PKD) was supposed to as in 33 way, without ideation within conscious. ness. (As I did with the ad.) But the process begun the day in Feb, the pentathos + Golden Fish, changed things. Thomas + his memories broke into [my] consciousness - would have without the Xerox missive coming. This is because, partly, \"Tears\" had just been pub‐ lished + I knew subliminally there was code - political code - in \"Tears\" + so knew that the contact would come",
