  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "Last edit almost 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n69\nNeeds Review\n69\n7 Eachy is me. Not Chris. But caus It's next to impossible to figure out the I truth (about yourself) from the of possible ones due to the scrambler, but: 1) info dump in my head. 3-74 2) other personality. 3-74 3) letter from red army intelligence 3-74 4) + the scrambler itself, is The Hegelian. Engels dialectic. 6) what do these as probably add up to? As Soviet agent who called bureau -fought self won. The religious stuff is cover",
      "matched_alias": "Hegelian",
      "term_id": "TERM_hegelian",
      "term_name": "Hegelian",
      "term_slug": "hegelian"
    },
    {
      "text": "Last edit almost 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n74\nNeeds Review\n74\n76 I submit that my \"anamnesis\" of a former life was actually a reacquiring of dissociated memories of some years back - hence the sense of them being archaic They were archaic - probably a decade or more back. the dialectic was specifically marxist - Engelsist. violent secret revolutionary group in the country of the enemy. Codes. Stealth + concealment essential fear of \"the Romans\" - i.e. the official authorities. those in power w",
      "matched_alias": "Paradise",
      "term_id": "TERM_paradise",
      "term_name": "Paradise",
      "term_slug": "paradise"
    }
